title: PM to inaugurate completed track of Karachi-Hyderabad Motorway today
text:
PM to inaugurate completed track of Karachi-Hyderabad Motorway today | 0 
KARACHI: Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif will inaugurate the completed portion of the Karachi-Hyderabad M9 motorway. 
The federal government has completed 50 percent of the Motorway and it is expected that the entire project will be completed by March 2018. 0 0 PM to inaugurate completed track of Karachi-Hyderabad Motorway today was posted in pakistan of Geo TV - https://www.geo.tv on February 03, 2017 and was last updated on February 03, 2017.
